Package: PI4AD
Type: Package
Title: Priority Index for Alzheimer's Disease
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-5-27
Authors@R: c(person("Hai", "Fang", email="fh12355@rjh.com.cn", role=c("aut","cre")))
Maintainer: Hai Fang <fh12355@rjh.com.cn>
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0), igraph, ggplot2
Imports: BiocGenerics, dplyr, forcats, GenomicRanges, ggnetwork, ggrepel, IRanges, Matrix, methods, osfr, purrr, stats, stringr, tibble, tidyr, pbapply, curl, ggraph
Suggests: grid, gridExtra, RColorBrewer, ggupset, MASS, graphics, grDevices, utils, ggbio, GenomeInfoDb, fgsea, scales, supraHex
Description: This package is developed as part of computational medicine efforts enabling multi-omics-led and network-driven therapeutic target prioritisation in the context of Alzheimer's disease (AD). Together with the showcase, this package promotes transparency and reproducibility, allowing users to build upon computational medicine and potentially contribute to the advancement of AD research.
